title: For Sale:  USGI M1 Carbine - National Postal Meter with Extras
postcontent:
Selling an M1 Carbine. If you have never shot one, you are missing a great experience and piece of our military history. This carbine is a National Postal Meter. It is an original USGI with no import marks and came from CMP a few years back. It has a low 1.4 million serial number so was made in middle of WWII. Stock is birch and is clean with only a few dings.

I am selling it with 50-rds ammo, two 30-round magazines, and a carbine pouch with two-15 round magazines (15-round mags are loaded with ammo). It also includes the sling and oiler.

Will also make available to buyer additional 15- and 30-round magazines and several boxes of carbine ammo at very reasonable prices if desired.
